{"tid":919210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【立法會會議直播】張宇人議員猛轟官員","createTime":"2018-11-28T01:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T15:17:02.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"572190c9bbea57208f1bbca6de4e265bfe9e5c0a","tid":919210,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:19:38.000Z","msg":"jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f018e84cd141fab6ee04a83af5b9a68fa6d535ee","tid":919210,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:22:12.000Z","msg":"工務小組委員會<br />\n2018年11月28日(星期三)上午8時30分至10時30分<br />\n在立法會綜合大樓會議室1舉行會議 <br />\n<br />\n議程<br />\n文件編號\t\t事項<br />\n總目705－土木工程<br />\n1.\tPWSC(2018-19)32*註釋符號代表2018年11月14日會議未完成審議而要順延的議程項目\t173DR\t有機資源回收中心第二期 <br />\n<br />\n(出席人員︰環境局副局長／環境保護署副署長(2)／環境保護署助理署長(廢物基建規劃)／環境保護署首席環境保護主任(廚餘回收)(署理)) <br />\n<br />\n(環境事務委員會已在2018年7月19日的會議上討論此項目。當局已向事務委員會提交補充資料文件CB(1)142/18-19(02)。) <br />\n<br />\n(范國威議員提出的書面問題(PWSC22/18-19(01))(只備中文本)(2018年11月13日發出)以及政府當局提交的資料文件(PWSC27/18-19(01)) (只備中文本) (2018年11月14日發出)) <br />\n<br />\n(工務小組委員會已在2018年11月14日的會議上討論此項目。) <br />\n<br />\n(許智峯議員提出的書面問題(PWSC32/18-19(01))(只備中文本)(2018年11月23日發出)) <br />\n<br />\n總目711－房屋<br />\n2.\tPWSC(2018-19)33\t75MC\t屯門第29區西社區健康中心暨安老院舍 <br />\n<br />\n(出席人員︰運輸及房屋局總土木工程師(工務計劃)／建築署工程策劃總監(2)／建築署高級工程策劃經理229／食物及衞生局首席助理秘書長(衞生)5／社會福利署助理署長(安老服務)／房屋署總建築師(2)／醫院管理局新界西醫院聯網服務總監(基層及社區醫療)) <br />\n<br />\n(房屋事務委員會已在2018年11月5日的會議上討論此項目。當局已向事務委員會提交補充資料文件CB(1)221/18-19(01)。)) <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(其他出席會議的公職人員：發展局常任秘書長(工務)／發展局常任秘書長(規劃及地政)／環境局常任秘書長) <br />\n<br />\n～完～<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/fc/pwsc/agenda/pwsc20181128.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fagenda%2Fpwsc20181128.htm&d=E1T%2B3%2Fwi7mooJkZ6DPK9TRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4df68576\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/fc/pwsc/agenda/pwsc20181128.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8b5eeaa1328200c230c6dfeec3b736884c38e6a8","tid":919210,"uid":66324,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:28:26.000Z","msg":"轟完又點? 咪又乖乖贊成政府ge野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5de5b676d75dafc88899ff96889e1adb116fd0","tid":919210,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b5eeaa1328200c230c6dfeec3b736884c38e6a8","tid":919210,"uid":66324,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:28:26.000Z","msg":"轟完又點? 咪又乖乖贊成政府ge野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a36b69806bbce58b0f0687df71fe9604bce8d7","tid":919210,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:37:28.000Z","msg":"易志明議員都圍攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2caf6adfbd9d7d40cbb67603809571a3b7f085aa","tid":919210,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:38:04.000Z","msg":"張宇人議員發火了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4f8b9ec94b595a4d762161f60a4e1b84e7f166","tid":919210,"uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:38:47.000Z","msg":"吹奏保皇黨是否焦土行為之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4694d192abdc19999071a3c09ece8528c07021aa","tid":919210,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":